external_knowledge:
- "Fertile fields of economic growth" refers to GDP, average wage, employment rate, and poverty rate;
- "Towering edifices of housing stability" alludes to median rent, vacancy rate, and housing units per 200% poverty level;
- "Bustling markets of investment" cover total investment, return on investment, and impact finance per 200% poverty level;
- "Nurturing grounds of community development" include the number of projects, total funding, and community development projects per 200% poverty level;
- "Innovative minds that shape the future" represent total workforce, skilled workforce percentage, and the innovation index.

sql:
SELECT counties.county_name, housing_data.average_home_value
FROM counties
INNER JOIN housing_data ON counties.county_id = housing_data.county_id;
